      • getHandler

        public SsoServerLoggingHdlrEntryImpl getHandler​(String handlerName)
        Provides the handle to the specific handler eg. DBHandler, FileHandler etc.
        Parameters:
        handlerName - String which acts as key to retrieve handler from the map. The allowed keys are DB_HANDLER_NAME, FILE_HANDLER_NAME etc.
        Returns:
        A null value may mean following: 1) The Agent is not running. 2) The parameter 'handlerName' is blank or null. 3) There is no entry in the handler map for the key handlerName i.e. it is an invalid key.
